{"tid":1653453,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"郭明錤預測iPhone SE 2 64GB $3,130","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T01:43:23.000Z","uid":178875,"like":11,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"139e4c25e4b4f141fdc556023b3483a977d52e9f","tid":1653453,"uid":178875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"雖然昨日是星期日，但無阻著名 Apple 分析師郭明錤撰文，根據他最新發表的研究報告，Apple 打算在 2020 年首季推出 iPhone SE 2，而且售價只需 399 美元起（折合 HK$3,130），如果屬實，相信香港上市的售價可能只需 HK$3,199 左右。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2019-10/14/214281/uniqlo_1_c7d7c613d09fe96678dc044e64b35f3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2019-10%2F14%2F214281%2Funiqlo_1_c7d7c613d09fe96678dc044e64b35f3c.jpg&h=d40dd0e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭明錤預測 iPhone SE 2：配備 A13 Bionic、64GB 儲存定價 $3,130<br />\n<br />\n郭明錤表示 iPhone SE 2 將會採用和 iPhone 11 相同的 A13 Bionic 處理器，搭配 3GB LPDDR4X RAM，並且有 64GB 和 128GB 兩種容量選擇。他又提到 Apple 將會重施 iPhone SE 時的故技，將舊機款的機身設計用於 iPhone SE 2，而新機的造型將會跟 iPhone 8 類似。<br />\n<br />\niPhone SE 2 將會有類似 iPhone 8 的機身設計，但就會將 3D Touch 功能移除，不過實體 Home 鍵和 Touch ID 指紋辨識則得以保留。Apple 將會提供太空灰、銀色和紅色 3 種機身配色選擇，郭明錤預計會吸引現有 iPhone 6 和 iPhone 6S 用戶升級換機。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：macrumors<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/214281/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F214281%2F1%2F&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DArZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=f151e9fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/214281/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望呢次真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3ae1eae4a3020b6e35135676bce4e15f3af6b0","tid":1653453,"uid":209543,"like":8,"dislike":29,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:39:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc0f5b6dadaad1970d67f9c549689069b24d7c21","tid":1653453,"uid":132941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit